{"tid":1888514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為控美國會違憲遭駁回","createTime":"2020-02-20T08:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T09:39:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c5a196a46f1c6476ac2f56f2288073c334877d","tid":1888514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200220/I4U33GCPDNBGAS4FOGI4E3WMYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200220%2FI4U33GCPDNBGAS4FOGI4E3WMYE%2F&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=eb0e972a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200220%2FI4U33GCPDNBGAS4FOGI4E3WMYE%2F&h=ea3071e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200220/I4U33GCPDNBGAS4FOGI4E3WMYE/</a><br />\n<br />\n華為控美國會違憲遭駁回<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200220/large/1582130076_c645.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200220%2Flarge%2F1582130076_c645.jpg&h=79652411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美就華為角力沒完沒了。<br />\n<br />\n中國電訊設備巨頭華為去年初入稟美國法院，指控美國會限制其與聯邦機構和承包商做生意的做法，違反美國憲法。當地時間18日，德州聯邦法官裁定駁回華為的訴訟，稱美國會有權做決定，禁止聯邦機構及其承包商從華為購買產品。華為公司回應稱，會繼續考慮採取進一步法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「東亞病夫」源於晚清思想家<br />\n<br />\n政府機構續禁華為<br />\n<br />\n2019年3月華為入稟美國法院，指美國會通過的《2019財年國防授權法》（National Defense Authorization Act）第889條，禁止聯邦機構和旗下承包商採購華為的設備和服務，「過份限制銷售和違反正當程序，違反美國憲法的精神」。路透社昨報道，德州聯邦法官馬贊特（Amos Mazzant）在一份長達57頁的裁決中作出上述裁決，駁回華為的訴訟。法官表示，華為仍可與美國其他公司開展業務。<br />\n<br />\n華為公司昨對該判決表示失望；華為的聲明指，「我們理解國家安全至關重要，但美國國會用國防授權法對華為進行限制的方式，只能為其提供虛假的安全感，且侵犯華為的憲法權利。我們對此感到失望。將考慮採取進一步法律行動。」美國司法部發言人對判決感到滿意。特朗普上台後，以美中貿易有巨大逆差為由，發起對華貿易戰。接着又以中國「竊取美國技術」為由，對華發起科技戰，中國中興和華為兩大電訊設備公司首當其衝。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美國之音"},{"pid":"fad2da33b61eb459c123e8bb4b5eb3a58c041788","tid":1888514,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:56:22.000Z","msg":"只是剛剛開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11051f2d3d254b7d6823e09fdd7a19ca72c2a6a5","tid":1888514,"uid":282118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:58:40.000Z","msg":"共產國家講憲法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等同太監開talk講做愛"},{"pid":"4f12952d0140527cf08e639b4db9aafa8773e856","tid":1888514,"uid":205462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"共匪一向都鍾意使橫手，偷外資公司嘅技術資產，家陣美國只不過係採取防盜措施，保障國家利益，你班臭蝗又去干涉他國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ae6cbefc5301cf83248954fa8c9f60b2479f06","tid":1888514,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7298ac6d00bd1d86aa973e5dcf4866a1d2623a6e","tid":1888514,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BJeDJX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BJeDJX.jpg&h=9becf84c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c46b75cf50c02ccaf1e0df88a39a1a230001872e","tid":1888514,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:26:51.000Z","msg":"簽完第一階段trade deal之後下下重擊<br />\n之前感覺trump為選舉讓步 估唔到咁快又出手"},{"pid":"781a45e7e22f5ba136be6c4c2523e8e190f08797","tid":1888514,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405409bb943e6d25be41ece5590cf023b0b7f37a","tid":1888514,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"god bless America"},{"pid":"dcdd5a3be39b2adfc93ee5e78dfa7b268d121f51","tid":1888514,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"華為呢間野就死梗<br />\n睇左咁多間傳媒, Trump係想整撚死呢間野"}]}